{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":45351,"originalJapaneseLine":"それでも――――","translatedEnglishLine":"Even so――――"},{"lineNumber":45352,"originalJapaneseLine":"「わ……わ、わた、私、っ……いや、っ……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I-I, I... n-no...\""},{"lineNumber":45353,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あんな風に殺されて……","translatedEnglishLine":"Killed like that...?"},{"lineNumber":45354,"originalJapaneseLine":"　それを、放送、されて、なんてっ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"And that was... broadcasted...!"},{"lineNumber":45355,"originalJapaneseLine":"耳にこびりつく、犠牲者達の絶叫。","translatedEnglishLine":"The victims' screams cling to my ears."},{"lineNumber":45356,"originalJapaneseLine":"命を賭けて仕えると誓った、敬愛する国王の、","translatedEnglishLine":"The beloved king, whom I swore to serve with my life,"},{"lineNumber":45357,"originalJapaneseLine":"ゴミのような死に顔が目蓋の裏から消えてくれない。","translatedEnglishLine":"His face, lifeless like trash, won't leave the back of my eyelids."},{"lineNumber":45358,"originalJapaneseLine":"「こ、こわい、よっ…………！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I-I'm scared...!\""},{"lineNumber":45359,"originalJapaneseLine":"友達の、暖かく柔らかい体温が伝わってくる。","translatedEnglishLine":"My friend's warm and soft body heat reaches me."},{"lineNumber":45360,"originalJapaneseLine":"それでも、フルーカの震えは強くなるばかりだった。","translatedEnglishLine":"Even so, Fluka's trembling only grew stronger."},{"lineNumber":45361,"originalJapaneseLine":"「大丈夫……大丈夫だよ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's alright... it'll be alright."},{"lineNumber":45362,"originalJapaneseLine":"　無事に生き残って……","translatedEnglishLine":"Survive safely..."},{"lineNumber":45363,"originalJapaneseLine":"　雷帝様に、一緒に叱られよ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"Then we'll be scolded together by the Thunder Emperor, okay?\""},{"lineNumber":45364,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うん…………う……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yeah... uh...\""},{"lineNumber":45365,"originalJapaneseLine":"扉が、優雅に開く音が、フルーカの頷きを止めた。","translatedEnglishLine":"The sound of the door opening gracefully stopped Fluka's nod."},{"lineNumber":45366,"originalJapaneseLine":"「失礼いたしますよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Excuse me.\""},{"lineNumber":45367,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ひ、ッ――――！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Eek――――!\""},{"lineNumber":45368,"originalJapaneseLine":"「だ、誰ッ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"W-who...?!\""},{"lineNumber":45369,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔軍の将、魔人メディウサの使い。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I am the demon army general, the envoy of the demon Medusa."},{"lineNumber":45370,"originalJapaneseLine":"　アレフガルドと申します」","translatedEnglishLine":"My name is Alefgard.\""},{"lineNumber":45371,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そんなっ……！　ここは20人くらいで","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No way...! There should have been about 20 of us defending here..."},{"lineNumber":45372,"originalJapaneseLine":"　守ってたはずなのに……」","translatedEnglishLine":"We were supposed to be protecting this place...\""},{"lineNumber":45373,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お休み頂いておりますよ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"They are all taking a rest."},{"lineNumber":45374,"originalJapaneseLine":"　皆様お疲れのようですな」","translatedEnglishLine":"They all seem quite exhausted.\""},{"lineNumber":45375,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ッ、く……！　雷げ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Gah...! Thunder..."},{"lineNumber":45376,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いけません」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No.\""},{"lineNumber":45377,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あっ…………！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah...!\""},{"lineNumber":45378,"originalJapaneseLine":"ナスティは手に生み出した魔力を放出する間もなく、","translatedEnglishLine":"Nasty collapsed onto the floor before she could release the magic she had summoned in her hand."},{"lineNumber":45379,"originalJapaneseLine":"床に倒れ伏した。","translatedEnglishLine":"She fell onto the floor."},{"lineNumber":45380,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ナスティ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Nasty!\""},

{"lineNumber":45381,"originalJapaneseLine":"「運が悪くなければ死にはしません。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"If you're not unlucky, you won't die."},

{"lineNumber":45382,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ごゆっくりお休みくださいませ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Please take a good rest.\""},{"lineNumber":45383,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………っ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...!\""},{"lineNumber":45384,"originalJapaneseLine":"慇懃に、執事を名乗る魔物がナスティに一礼する。","translatedEnglishLine":"The creature, calling itself a butler, politely bowed to Nasty."},{"lineNumber":45385,"originalJapaneseLine":"その動き。鋭さ。","translatedEnglishLine":"Its movement. Its sharpness."},{"lineNumber":45386,"originalJapaneseLine":"フルーカは雷軍の小隊長を務める身にも関わらず、","translatedEnglishLine":"Despite Fluka being a squad leader of the Thunder Army,"},{"lineNumber":45387,"originalJapaneseLine":"歴然とした戦力差を自覚せざるを得なかった。","translatedEnglishLine":"she couldn't help but realize the obvious gap in power."},{"lineNumber":45388,"originalJapaneseLine":"「さぁ……参りましょう。我が主がお待ちです」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Now... let us go. Our master is waiting.\""},{"lineNumber":45389,"originalJapaneseLine":"あくまで優雅に、アレフガルドが歩み寄る。","translatedEnglishLine":"Alefgard gracefully approached without haste."},{"lineNumber":45390,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや……いや、ッ……！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No... no...!\""},{"lineNumber":45391,"originalJapaneseLine":"　つっ……つかまる、くらいならッ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'd rather... be captured than this...!\""},{"lineNumber":45392,"originalJapaneseLine":"フルーカの手に魔力が収束する。","translatedEnglishLine":"Magic power gathered in Fluka's hand."},{"lineNumber":45393,"originalJapaneseLine":"そして、その手を自らの胸に押し当てる。","translatedEnglishLine":"Then she pressed that hand firmly against her chest."},{"lineNumber":45394,"originalJapaneseLine":"涙が溢れる目を強く閉じて、覚悟を決めた。","translatedEnglishLine":"With tear-filled eyes, she closed them tightly and steeled herself."},{"lineNumber":45395,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ライトニング……レーザー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Lightning... Laser!\""},{"lineNumber":45396,"originalJapaneseLine":"「う……あ、あ、あぁ…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ugh... ah, ah, aaaah...\""},{"lineNumber":45397,"originalJapaneseLine":"天井が射貫かれ、風穴が空いた。","translatedEnglishLine":"The ceiling was pierced, leaving a hole to the wind."},{"lineNumber":45398,"originalJapaneseLine":"手首を掴み上げたアレフガルドが、","translatedEnglishLine":"Alefgard, who had grabbed her wrist,"},{"lineNumber":45399,"originalJapaneseLine":"フルーカににっこりと微笑みかける。","translatedEnglishLine":"smiled gently at Fluka."},{"lineNumber":45400,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お嬢様へのプレゼント。」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"A gift for the young lady.\""}]}

